title: George Carlin Standup Comedy Video Collection
description:
A collection of George Carlin standup comedy videos (mostly HBO features) including:

1. Life is Worth Losing (2005)
2. Complaints and Grievances (2001)
3. You Are All Diseased (1999)
4. Jammin&#039; in NY (1992)
5. Doin&#039; It Again (1990)
6. Carlin at Carnegie (1982)
7. George Carlin Again! (1978)
8. An Evening with George Carlin (1977)

Note:
Total size of the videos is just a little bit over the capacity of an average DVD-R (4,483 MB) so if you&#039;re gonna burn it, make sure your burning software (such as Nero) is configured for overburning.
